8b62398be15","tid":376244,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 做開二手 我想問 <br />\nrolex一般若干年份同佢本身個價值會有幾保值<br />\n我第一次買 屋企人有戴開d普通有石款<br />\n即係專門店買到個d<br />\n<br />\n我今次買隻地通拿 幾年後係咪都有幾折價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋要唔要好小心戴 易唔易花 要唔要定期清洗下錶帶之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n運動款先保值(gmt,十仔個d)<br />\n咩16233，69173，77080，個d成熟款都輸得多，當然啦要睇你咩價位入，如果你宜家入這隻一定輸得唔多，雖然你超超公價入，但應該都算輸得少個炸，小心個外圈啦，整爆左要成個換非常貴，間唔中帶下佢唔帶都郁下佢"},{"pid":"f5b82012d91b326ca8286e3721b318bb25162461","tid":376244,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打 <br />\n屋企有個錶盒<br />\n聽人講set轉得密未必好 <br />\n話加快磨損同壽命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪真<br />\n外圈會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁脆弱架原來"},{"pid":"42f7ae5e183518a72c03278ff774b96286b63228","tid":376244,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該巴打 <br />\n屋企有個錶盒<br />\n聽人講set轉得密未必好 <br />\n話加快磨損同壽命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪真<br />\n外圈會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁脆弱架原來</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最好間唔中手調下佢，自動錶盒好像無咩需要"},{"pid":"42a550af9366e4ec0552d79c9e324635adeaf44c","tid":376244,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"佢地唔係成日戴<br />\n覺得次次戴都要調同上鏈好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1313f6c8b3c7c3e2b2d72e3c7c5821aa27f6c09a","tid":376244,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地唔係成日戴<br />\n覺得次次戴都要調同上鏈好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔洗日日上鏈，一頭半個月郁下佢就得"},{"pid":"d6e8cf57a2f8562b9362a5b34ed0e4dd88c87145","tid":376244,"uid":18886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地唔係成日戴<br />\n覺得次次戴都要調同上鏈好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買左了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acf6055627ff54dec33cd8e3d3cb7b475211187","tid":376244,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"唔係幾日唔戴就停啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}